Variables :
---------------------------

Its a container to hold some data that can be used by the program



How tp decalre a Variable:

var yourvar name  = yourvale

var
----- after 2015 
let
const


// var 

// u can reassign and redeclare 

//redclare
var totals = '123';
var totals = 'wwww'
//reassign
var totals = '123';
totals = 'wwww'


// let  

// u can not redeclare in same scope
// but u can redeclare in different scope
// but u can reassign 


// const   

// u cannot do reassign
// u can redeclare in different scope



Data type :-------

number - 12233
string - 'sdddd'
boolean - true/false
array -  []
object - {}

